{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS Phase 3 S03 metadata-prep diagnostics validation. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.19.6 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-19 #}

{# =========================
  Phase 3 S03 Metadata-Prep Validation (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: deterministic diagnostics verdict for metadata handoff readiness without metadata ownership cutover.
  Usage: run after `spectra_ls.run_p3_s03_sequence` (or `validate_metadata_prep`).
  Note: explicit static entity watchers below are intentional so HA template dependency tracking
        subscribes to updates for both shadow sensor naming variants.
  ========================= #}

{# Static watcher anchors for HA dependency tracking (do not remove). #}
{% set watch_shadow_target_state = states.sensor.shadow_active_target.state if states.sensor.shadow_active_target is not none else 'missing' %}
{% set watch_shadow_target_captured_at = state_attr('sensor.shadow_active_target', 'captured_at') | default('missing', true) %}
{% set watch_shadow_path_state = states.sensor.shadow_active_control_path.state if states.sensor.shadow_active_control_path is not none else 'missing' %}
{% set watch_shadow_path_captured_at = state_attr('sensor.shadow_active_control_path', 'captured_at') | default('missing', true) %}
{% set watch_legacy_target_state = states.sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target.state if states.sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target is not none else 'missing' %}
{% set watch_legacy_target_captured_at = state_attr('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target', 'captured_at') | default('missing', true) %}
{% set watch_legacy_path_state = states.sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path.state if states.sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path is not none else 'missing' %}
{% set watch_legacy_path_captured_at = state_attr('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path', 'captured_at') | default('missing', true) %}
{% set watcher_checksum = (
  watch_shadow_target_state ~ '|' ~
  watch_shadow_target_captured_at ~ '|' ~
  watch_shadow_path_state ~ '|' ~
  watch_shadow_path_captured_at ~ '|' ~
  watch_legacy_target_state ~ '|' ~
  watch_legacy_target_captured_at ~ '|' ~
  watch_legacy_path_state ~ '|' ~
  watch_legacy_path_captured_at
) %}

{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}
{% set freshness_required_s = 300 %}

{% set metadata = state_attr(s_target, 'metadata_prep_validation') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set selection = state_attr(s_target, 'selection_handoff_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}

{% set verdict = metadata.verdict if metadata is mapping and metadata.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set ready = metadata.ready_for_metadata_handoff if metadata is mapping and metadata.ready_for_metadata_handoff is defined else false %}

{% set missing_required = metadata.missing_required if metadata is mapping and metadata.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set checks = metadata.checks if metadata is mapping and metadata.checks is defined and metadata.checks is mapping else {} %}
{% set values = metadata.values if metadata is mapping and metadata.values is defined and metadata.values is mapping else {} %}

{% set check_active_meta = checks.active_meta_entity_resolved if checks.active_meta_entity_resolved is defined else false %}
{% set check_now_playing_entity = checks.now_playing_entity_resolved if checks.now_playing_entity_resolved is defined else false %}
{% set check_now_playing_state = checks.now_playing_state_resolved if checks.now_playing_state_resolved is defined else false %}
{% set check_now_playing_title = checks.now_playing_title_resolved if checks.now_playing_title_resolved is defined else false %}
{% set check_candidates = checks.candidate_payload_ready if checks.candidate_payload_ready is defined else false %}
{% set check_route_trace = checks.route_trace_present if checks.route_trace_present is defined else false %}

{% set probe_active_meta = values.active_meta_entity if values.active_meta_entity is defined and values.active_meta_entity != 'missing' else states('sensor.ma_active_meta_entity') %}
{% set probe_now_playing_entity = values.now_playing_entity if values.now_playing_entity is defined and values.now_playing_entity != 'missing' else states('sensor.now_playing_entity') %}
{% set probe_now_playing_state = values.now_playing_state if values.now_playing_state is defined and values.now_playing_state != 'missing' else states('sensor.now_playing_state') %}
{% set probe_now_playing_title = values.now_playing_title if values.now_playing_title is defined and values.now_playing_title != 'missing' else states('sensor.now_playing_title') %}

{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set selection_verdict = selection.verdict if selection is mapping and selection.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target,'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set captured_age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set snapshot_fresh = captured_age_s is not none and captured_age_s <= freshness_required_s %}

{% set effective_verdict = verdict %}
{% if verdict == 'PASS' and not snapshot_fresh %}
  {% set effective_verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% elif verdict == 'missing' and not snapshot_fresh %}
  {% set effective_verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% endif %}

{% set gate_count = 0 %}
{% if check_active_meta %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if check_now_playing_entity %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if check_now_playing_state %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if check_now_playing_title %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if check_candidates %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if check_route_trace %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if contract_valid %}{% set gate_count = gate_count + 1 %}{% endif %}

### Phase 3 S03 Metadata-Prep Validation (`spectra_ls`)
- Result: **{{ effective_verdict }}** (base={{ verdict }})
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**
- Ready for metadata handoff: **{{ ready }}**
- Gate score: **{{ gate_count }}/7**

### Runtime context
- Active target (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ states(s_target) }}**
- Active path (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ states(s_path) }}**
- Route decision: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Selection handoff verdict: **{{ selection_verdict }}**
- Write authority mode: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- Snapshot fresh (<= {{ freshness_required_s }}s): **{{ snapshot_fresh }}** (age={{ (captured_age_s | round(1)) if captured_age_s is not none else 'n/a' }}s)

### Metadata value probes
- Active meta entity: **{{ probe_active_meta if probe_active_meta is not none else 'missing' }}**
- Now playing entity: **{{ probe_now_playing_entity if probe_now_playing_entity is not none else 'missing' }}**
- Now playing state: **{{ probe_now_playing_state if probe_now_playing_state is not none else 'missing' }}**
- Now playing title: **{{ probe_now_playing_title if probe_now_playing_title is not none else 'missing' }}**

### Gate breakdown
- Contract valid: **{{ contract_valid }}**
- Active meta entity resolved: **{{ check_active_meta }}**
- Now playing entity resolved: **{{ check_now_playing_entity }}**
- Now playing state resolved: **{{ check_now_playing_state }}**
- Now playing title resolved: **{{ check_now_playing_title }}**
- Metadata candidates payload ready: **{{ check_candidates }}**
- Route-trace present: **{{ check_route_trace }}**

### Contract details
- Missing required metadata entities: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- Missing keys: **{{ missing_required }}**
- Listener checksum (debug): **{{ watcher_checksum | length }} chars**

### Listener anchors (debug)
- `sensor.shadow_active_target`: **{{ states('sensor.shadow_active_target') }}** (captured_at={{ state_attr('sensor.shadow_active_target','captured_at') | default('missing', true) }})
- `sensor.shadow_active_control_path`: **{{ states('sensor.shadow_active_control_path') }}** (captured_at={{ state_attr('sensor.shadow_active_control_path','captured_at') | default('missing', true) }})
- `sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target`: **{{ states('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target') }}** (captured_at={{ state_attr('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target','captured_at') | default('missing', true) }})
- `sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path`: **{{ states('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path') }}** (captured_at={{ state_attr('sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path','captured_at') | default('missing', true) }})
- `sensor.ma_active_meta_entity`: **{{ states('sensor.ma_active_meta_entity') }}**
- `sensor.now_playing_entity`: **{{ states('sensor.now_playing_entity') }}**
- `sensor.now_playing_state`: **{{ states('sensor.now_playing_state') }}**
- `sensor.now_playing_title`: **{{ states('sensor.now_playing_title') }}**
- `sensor.ma_meta_candidates` best candidate: **{{ state_attr('sensor.ma_meta_candidates','best_candidate_json') | default('missing', true) }}**

### Recommendation
{% if effective_verdict == 'PASS' %}
- Metadata-prep diagnostics are healthy.
- Keep ownership in compatibility mode for now and proceed to Phase-4 planning slice.
{% elif effective_verdict == 'WARN' %}
- Metadata-prep is partially healthy; stabilize WARN gates before any ownership discussions.
- Do **not** cut over metadata ownership yet.
{% else %}
- Metadata-prep is not ready. Resolve FAIL gates and rerun this template.
- Keep legacy runtime as metadata source-of-truth.
{% endif %}
